data.description: Discover the perfect fusion of updated style and convenience in this beautifully, fully renovated ranch home located in Atlanta's vibrant and sought-after Grove Park neighborhood. This property, set at 364 New Jersey Avenue, offers a unique blend of city living and suburban comfort. Step inside to find a welcoming open-plan layout, with ample natural light pouring in through large windows. The living space is perfect for both relaxing and entertaining, featuring high-quality finishes and contemporary design. The heart of this home is its stunning kitchen, equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, sleek countertops, and plenty of cabinet space. It's an ideal spot for both cooking enthusiasts and for hosting friends and family. The property boasts four bedrooms, each offering a personal retreat and a bonus room that can be used as an office or additional bedroom. The bathrooms are modern, featuring high-end fixtures and elegant tiling. Enjoy Atlanta's beautiful weather in your private backyard or charming front porch, perfect for outdoor dining, entertaining or simply relaxing. Situated just inside the Perimeter, this home is conveniently located near the new Westside Park, top-rated schools, shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment. Plus, it's just a short drive from downtown Atlanta, offering the best of the city at your doorstep. Offering the perfect balance of luxury and comfort, this property is waiting for you to make it your own. Schedule a visit today and experience firsthand the charm and convenience of this Atlanta gem!
